lyrics:
[Verse 1]
In the shadows of my mind, secrets reside
Locked away, hidden deep, I cannot confide
Whispers echo, haunting my soul's darkest night
But I'll keep my silence, the truth I'll continue to hide

[Chorus]
Oh, these secrets, heavy burdens on my heart
Tears flow silently, tearing me apart
Chasing after solace, but finding no release
Oh, these secrets, they bind me like a masterpiece
